== Music ==

The film has songs composed by [[Yuvan Shankar Raja]], two of which have been re-mixed from the original film, which had [[M. S. Viswanathan]] as the music composer:

* "My Name is Billa" - [[S. P. Balasubramaniam]]
* "Vethialaya Pottendy" - [[Malaysia Vasudevan]]

== Trivia == 

*[[Don (film)|Don]], the [[Bollywood]] blockbuster of the [[1980s]], was remade with contemporary idioms recently in Bollywood.

*The original [[Don]] was remade in [[Tamil]] in the [[1980s]] as [[Billa (1980 film)|Billa]].

*Billa is now being remade and reinvented in Tamil.

*Getting into the act will be [[Ajith Kumar]]. And directing it will be [[Vishnuvardhan]], the modern Tamil director.

*[[L. Suresh Balaji]] of Ananda Pictures will produce this film. [[Nirav Shah]] will handle the camera. [[Yuvan Shankar Raja]] will score the music.

*[[Shahrukh Khan]]<U+2019>s [[Don (2006 film)|Don]] is a big hit. In fact, such remakes are now the norm in [[Bollywood]].

*To make a [[Rajini]] movie as a remake takes guts and strength of character. And [[Ajith]] has shown that he has it in him.

*[[Ajith Kumar]] has also got the go-ahead from [[Rajini]].

*The film will begin rolling in [[March]] [[2007]].

*[[Vishnuvardhan]], sources claim, had been toying with this idea for long.


